# cPanel License Activation


cPanel license can be issued from windows test server. Open 64.235.52.120:5252 in RDP and log in to windows server

Then open cPanel management interface using firefox

**IMPORTANT NOTE**

- When you log-out from windows test server 64.235.52.120 then means sure you really log-out windows correctly. Don't just close rdp session otherwise it will keep open and next person will get terminal service error.
- Make sure you close firefox before logout since if one person is using firefox then other person cannot use at the same time in windows.
